data.text: @ChelseaBeach There was No queue jumping!? Haven’t we learned anything from this past year? We need to support & stand by one another. I focus on the positive & what happened for me was just that. God bless anyone who gets the vaccine & take a step toward safety & ending this pandemic.
@SagePonchie @Jennife11432669 @ChelseaBeach Ok fair enough. She did not have the correct info either..

@Jennife11432669 @WoofMeow604 @ChelseaBeach I didn’t do it for you. Lol. I followed up with this person because going around policing it and shaming vaccine cancellation waitlist results in wasted vaccines.

@WoofMeow604 @ChelseaBeach Me too! I was sharing to let others know And I’d encourage anyone who wants a vaccine to head to a clinic near the end of the day or go early & see about getting on a cancel/leftover list.
@WoofMeow604 @SagePonchie @ChelseaBeach Yes totally.
@SagePonchie @Jennife11432669 @ChelseaBeach 🤷‍♀️ don't really care. Lol. She seemed so angry for some reason that someone else got a shot.
@ChelseaBeach @WoofMeow604 @Jennife11432669 I don’t think crawling Twitter and policing it yourself is the answer either.
@WoofMeow604 @Jennife11432669 @ChelseaBeach I’m on it. Lol
@Jennife11432669 @ChelseaBeach I am glad you were able to get a shot. We would hate them to be wasted (hopefully that never happens!!)
@Jennife11432669 @ChelseaBeach Oh how nice of her to block me when I was giving her the correct info. Lol.

@ChelseaBeach @WoofMeow604 Being on standby list at at a vaccination site is NOT a new thing. Ppl have been doing this since the rollout. They would be thrown out if an arm wasn’t able to take the dose. These extra vaccines are only given out when appts are all over.
@WoofMeow604 @ChelseaBeach They actually had a list when they put my name down there were others who’d done the same. They do have to be thrown out if ppl don’t show up.
@ChelseaBeach @WoofMeow604 For my husband thats how it worked. I called Saturday  morning & they booked him for Sunday just before noon
@ChelseaBeach @Jennife11432669 https://t.co/UvPf0Sgwen https://t.co/ccZziP8KvD
@WoofMeow604 @Jennife11432669 You also don't book your appt the day ahead & get in. Also, I didn't ask you. Thought you were genuinely trying to be helpful.

@ChelseaBeach @Jennife11432669 If they don't use them up they have to throw them away. It's hardly queue jumping. It's not like they have the resources to call eligible ppl to ask if they could come at the last min.
@WoofMeow604 @Jennife11432669 Thank you. I have a while to wait to be eligible. I asked the question as this person's bio doesn't look like she is over 75. Queue jumping shouldn't be happening.
@ChelseaBeach @Jennife11432669 They are booking for over 75 now. Also if you are indigenous person I think the age criteria is 55+.
@Jennife11432669 That’s great!
@Jennife11432669 Curious..Are you & your husband over 80?
@Katerin22434959 Thank you So much. I still can’t believe it. #Moderna
@Jennife11432669 So so happy for you!!!!
